The paper deals with optimization problems and their solutions using semi-definite programming (SDP) and logical formulas. Therefore, cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are likely categories. The paper also involves counting logic, which falls under cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the paper deals with constraint satisfaction problems, which are a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
